ğŸ’¡ **Tips to remember:**

* Always **make a temporary backup branch first** if you have uncommitted changes.
* Never `git reset --hard` unless you are sure you donâ€™t need your changes.
* `temp-save` is your â€œinsurance branchâ€ â€” you can always recover your work from it.

